Package: ancovEE
Title: ANCOVA-Based Energy Expenditure Analysis for Mouse Metabolic Phenotyping
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Your", "Name", email = "your@email.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
URL: https://github.com/akumar901/ancovEE
BugReports: https://github.com/akumar901/ancovEE/issues
Description: A toolkit for mouse metabolic phenotyping energy expenditure (EE)
    analysis following the NIDDK Mouse Metabolic Phenotyping Centers (MMPC)
    framework. The package provides a step-by-step workflow: (1) parsing NMR
    body composition data from Bruker minispec Excel exports, (2) preparing
    input files for ANCOVA analysis, and (3) running ANCOVA-based EE adjustment
    for body mass/composition covariates including detection of group-by-mass
    interactions and Johnson-Neyman cutoffs.
